value.name: Man Killed In Police Shootout Was Wanted For Hate Crime
value.description: Peter D'oech reports the FBI and a police task force tried to apprehend Alexander Carballido who was wanted for sexually assaulting a man during a home invasion.

value.name: WEB EXTRA: Ex-Con Pistol Whips, Robs Man Before Getting Into Deadly Shootout With Police
value.description: Ex-con pistol whips and robs a man in home invasion before getting into shootout with police. The suspect, Alexander Carballido, was killed. Nobody else was hurt despite hundreds of rounds being ...
